OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFrance sets out plan to ban
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdisposable vapes           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, France is set to ban disposable        
OL,6, e-cigarettes - known locally as "puffs"
OL,7, - because of the danger they pose to   
OL,8, the environment and public health.     
OL,10,FSpeaking recently on RTL radio, Prime  
OL,11,FMinister Elisabeth Borne said the      
OL,12,Fmeasure was part of a new anti-smoking 
OL,13,Fplan being drawn up by the government. 
OL,14,FIt should be in force by the end of the
OL,15,Fyear, campaigners said.                
OL,17,FSeveral other countries in Europe,     
OL,18,Fincluding Germany, Belgium and Ireland,
OL,19,Fhave announced similar bans. The UK is 
OL,20,Falso said to be considering one.       
